Welcome to the Minitrooper Middleweight Belt!

This competition is open to any army with a power rating of 150 or below.
You may challenge the current belt holder as many times as you like. If you win then post the replay in this thread and you become the new champion.
Only "Select an army base to infiltrate:" replays count. Replays where there URL ends in BAT1, BAT2, BAT3, MISS1, MISS2 or MISS3 are not allowed.
If you notice that the current belt holder has upgraded and now has power rating above 150 then you can immediately post in this thread to claim the belt for yourself without a fight.
Good luck everyone.

First person to post below with an army of power rating 150 or below will pick up the belt and get things rolling.
